nl.tudelft.dnainator.javafx.services

Class GraphLoadService

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.concurrent.Service<Graph>
      • nl.tudelft.dnainator.javafx.services.GraphLoadService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.concurrent.Worker<Graph>, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class GraphLoadService
extends javafx.concurrent.Service<Graph>
    A JavaFX background service to load files into graphs.

    Please note that none of the properties are initialized (beyond being set to null) upon instantiation.
